---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body class="bg-background text-foreground transition-colors duration-300">
		<Header />
		<main class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert lg:prose-xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
			<section class="space-y-6">
				<h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">
					Senior Frontend Engineer & Testing Automation Specialist
				</h1>
				<p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
					我是 Yusong，一名專注於高效能、可擴展性及自動化測試的資深前端工程師。我致力於透過卓越的架構設計與自動化流程，打造極致的開發體驗與穩定可靠的 Web 應用。
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="mt-12 space-y-8">
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold border-b pb-2">核心專長</h2>
					<ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 list-none p-0 mt-4">
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<span class="text-blue-500 font-bold">✓</span>
							<span><strong>現代化前端架構</strong>：精通 React 與 TypeScript，設計兼具靈活性與可維護性的系統。</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<span class="text-blue-500 font-bold">✓</span>
							<span><strong>自動化測試深度整合</strong>：深耕 Playwright 與視覺回歸測試，優化平行測試效率與報表可讀性。</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<span class="text-blue-500 font-bold">✓</span>
							<span><strong>CI/CD 流程優化</strong>：設計高效、穩定的開發與部署流水線。</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<span class="text-blue-500 font-bold">✓</span>
							<span><strong>AI 友善架構</strong>：構建易於 AI 理解與協作的代碼結構，提升開發效率 (DX)。</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold border-b pb-2">近期關注</h2>
					<p>
						目前我正致力於將 Progressive Web App (PWA) 與 Push Notifications 技術發揮到極致，並持續探索如何透過 AI 驅動的工具來重塑前端開發工作流。
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="mt-12 text-center sm:text-left">
				<p class="italic text-muted-foreground">
					"追求卓越不只是目標，而是一種持續優化的開發習慣。"
				</p>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
